casebody.data:
The PEOPLE etc., Respondent,
v.
Derrick ULETT, Appellant. Motion No: 2019-410 Court of Appeals of New York. Decided May 2, 2019

Motion by The Bronx Defenders, et al. for leave to file a brief amici curiae on the appeal herein granted and the proposed brief is accepted as filed. The brief must **729be submitted in digital format within seven days.
